        {
            "id": 6169378,
            "title": "〈台股盤後〉連假前重跌443點失守2萬6關 周K線收黑吐出全周漲點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>關稅雜音再起，美國總統川普宣布 10 月 1 日起對藥品、家具以及卡車等領域課徵關稅，加上接下來連假密集，台股今 (26) 日殺聲隆隆，一度跌逾 500 點，最低跌至 25469.04 點，終場跌 443.53 點或 1.7%，失守 26000 點關卡，也同步摜破 5 日線及 10 日線，成交量 4797.47 億元。 </p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6169378/l/ccad2b3e666d90ca5dd3ed85b18b1115.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">連假前關稅雜音再起，台股重挫逾400點失守2萬6關收25580點。(圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>川普寄出關稅三連發，宣布 10 月 1 日起，對所有品牌或專利藥品課徵 100% 關稅，此外，對所有廚櫃、浴室盥洗台等產品課徵 50% 關稅，也對重型卡車課徵 25% 關稅。消息一出，台股今日跌 443.53 點，吐出全周漲點僅剩 1.95 點，周 K 線翻黑，中止連四紅，並拉出長達 814 點的上影線。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>電子權值今天幾乎全數收黑，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 跌 20 元，收 1300 元，跌幅 1.52%，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>)、台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>) 跌幅沈重，雙雙跌逾 4%，聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 跌逾 2%，日月光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3711-TW</a>) 跌逾 3%，廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>) 則收平盤。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>資金瞄準高價千金股撤離，僅穎崴 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6515:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6515\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6515-TW</a>) 獨撐，漲逾 4%，股王信驊 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5274:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5274\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5274-TW</a>) 跌逾 2%，力旺 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3529:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3529\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3529-TW</a>)、弘塑 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3131:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3131\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3131-TW</a>) 及 AES-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6781:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6781\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6781-TW</a>) 跌逾半根停板。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>其他如川湖 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2059:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2059\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2059-TW</a>)、緯穎 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6669:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6669\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6669-TW</a>)、大立光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3008:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3008\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3008-TW</a>)、精測 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6510:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6510\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6510-TW</a>)、旺矽 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6223:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6223\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6223-TW</a>)、嘉澤 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3533:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3533\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3533-TW</a>)、祥碩 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5269:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5269\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5269-TW</a>)、創意 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3443:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3443\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3443-TW</a>)、台光電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2383:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2383\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2383-TW</a>) 及印能科技 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7734:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7734\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7734-TW</a>) 皆有 1 至 4% 不等的跌幅。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>不過被動元件無畏台股下殺，蜜望實 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8043:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8043\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8043-TW</a>)、斐成 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3313:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3313\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3313-TW</a>)、信昌電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6173:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6173\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6173-TW</a>) 攜手攻漲停，聚鼎 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6224:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6224\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6224-TW</a>) 漲逾半根停板，華新科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2492:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2492\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2492-TW</a>) 漲逾 4%，華容 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5328:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5328\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5328-TW</a>)、大毅 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2478:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2478\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2478-TW</a>) 也都有超過 1% 的漲幅。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
